long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Access all the content related to a Minecraft server Fox Craft. You can access their main website, store and join their discord with a few clicks. 
Also you can easily vote by clicking the vote links.
Useful for players of Fox Craft.
